!
! Description:
!   This blocklist protects users from phishing domains by blocking access to malicious sites.
!   It is regularly updated by our automation and community members.
!
! Get Involved:
!   Help us improve! Report phishing domains, false positives, or suggest improvements
!   by opening an issue or pull request on GitHub. Every contribution makes a difference!
!
! Usage:
!   Import this list into your adblocker (such as uBlock Origin or Adblock Plus)
!   to enhance your protection against phishing attacks.
!
! Disclaimer:
!   This list is provided as-is, without warranty. Use at your own risk.
!   For issues or false positives, please open an issue or submit a pull request.
